<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
  <head>
    <title>CSS Writing Modes Test: inline alignment - Text Baseline (horizontal layout with alphabetical alignment)</title>
    <link rel="author" title="Hajime Shiozawa" href="mailto:hajime.shiozawa@gmail.com" />
    <link rel="help" title="CSS3 Writing modes: 4.2. Text Baseline" href="http://www.w3.org/TR/css3-writing-modes/#text-baselines" />
    <meta name="assert" content="This tests a basic inline text alignment. Check that an alphabetical baseline is used as the dominant baseline." />
    <style type="text/css"><![CDATA[
      div > p {
        font-size: 2em;
        background-color: orange;
      }
      div > p > img {
        margin-left: -200px;
      }

      /* writing-mode property */
      .horizontal-tb {
        writing-mode: horizontal-tb;
      }

      /* text-orientation property */
      .mixed {
        text-orientation: mixed;
      }
      .upright {
        text-orientation: upright;
      }
      .sideways-right {
        text-orientation: sideways-right;
      }
      .sideways-left {
        text-orientation: sideways-left;
      }
      .sideways {
        text-orientation: sideways;
      }
      .use-glyph-orientation {
        text-orientation: use-glyph-orientation;
      }
  ]]></style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>Test passes if the bottom of glyph 'L' and the blue line are aligned.</p>
    <div class="horizontal-tb">
      <p class="mixed">LLLLLLLLLLLL<img src="./support/baseline.png" alt="baseline" width="220px" height="1px" /></p>
      <p class="upright">LLLLLLLLLLLL<img src="./support/baseline.png" alt="baseline" width="220px" height="1px" /></p>
      <p class="sideways-right">LLLLLLLLLLLL<img src="./support/baseline.png" alt="baseline" width="220px" height="1px" /></p>
      <p class="sideways-left">LLLLLLLLLLLL<img src="./support/baseline.png" alt="baseline" width="220px" height="1px" /></p>
      <p class="sideways">LLLLLLLLLLLL<img src="./support/baseline.png" alt="baseline" width="220px" height="1px" /></p>
      <p class="use-glyph-orientation">LLLLLLLLLLLL<img src="./support/baseline.png" alt="baseline" width="220px" height="1px" /></p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
